INSTALL
=======

1. Copy esuarezsantanarc to ~/.esuarezsantanarc
+
......................
$ cp esuarezsantanarc ~/.esuarezsantanarc
......................

2. Modify parameters of ~/.esuarezsantanarc as needed
+
......................
$ vim ~/.esuarezsantanarc
......................

3. Add the path of the scripts to the variable PYTHONPATH
+
......................
$ export PYTHONPATH=${PYTHONPATH}:`pwd`
......................

4. Add the path of the scripts to the variable PATH
+
......................
$ export PATH=${PATH}:`pwd`
......................

5. Add executable permissions to the scripts
+
......................
$ chmod +x *.py
......................


Utilities
---------

=== systamp ===

systamp needs a 'bonsai' directory to be created. This directory is

 $ systamp -p



